dc_title_s: Africa : corrected from observations of Mess. of ye Royal Societies at London and Paris
dc_description_s: Decorative title cartouche depicting animals.; Dedication: To Owen Brigstocke of Lechdony in the County of Carmarthen.; Shows boundaries, rivers, forests and principal settlements, with tents symbolising areas inhabited by nomads, and notes.; Relief shown pictorially.; London meridian.|69 x 98 centimeters|Scale [1:10,000,000]|General Map Collection
